"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"Post你d code出黎望下先"},{"pid":"218f5816626dbd666fc6271e26d5ff9fc744a576","tid":317830,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近開始玩React<br />\n我覺得個Concept幾易明直接<br />\n用起嚟幾就手，基本上多數嘢都係Plain JS嚟<br />\n易用，不過暫時我都仲係覺得好難寫得靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己寫唔寫得靚我唔太在意(反正都係寫畀自己睇!), 反而在意React堆3rd-party components library有冇自己想要嘅嘢:<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/brillout/awesome-react-components\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fbrillout%2Fawesome-react-components&d=8BBDh6HsE5LcO4ODcw7cS9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=51d802d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/brillout/awesome-react-components</a><br />\nAnyway, 有大堆components可用, 算唔錯架啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7003aaa457f7f45f43575c63d5e597c5abbe6ea5","tid":317830,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最近開始玩React<br />\n我覺得個Concept幾易明直接<br />\n用起嚟幾就手，基本上多數嘢都係Plain JS嚟<br />\n易用，不過暫時我都仲係覺得好難寫得靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己寫唔寫得靚我唔太在意(反正都係寫畀自己睇!), 反而在意React堆3rd-party components library有冇自己想要嘅嘢:<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/brillout/awesome-react-components\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fbrillout%2Fawesome-react-components&d=8BBDh6HsE5LcO4ODcw7cS9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=51d802d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/brillout/awesome-react-components</a><br />\nAnyway, 有大堆components可用, 算唔錯架啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係現成嘢比較多，Prototype都快手啲"},{"pid":"e3a698fb598ea2872b3fc1238561a991a219aaaa","tid":317830,"uid":108937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T18:11:03.000Z","